export default function Login() {
  return (<>
    <form
      className="popup__form"
      name="login-form"
    >
      <input
        required=""
        name="email"
        className="popup__input"
        placeholder="Email"
        defaultValue={''}
      />
      <input
        required=""
        name="password"
        className="popup__input"
        type="password"
        placeholder="Пароль"
        defaultValue={''}
      />
      <button
        className="popup__button"
        type="submit"
        aria-label="Войти"
      >
        Войти
      </button>
    </form>
  </>)
}
